title: Touhou Soundtracks 6-15 (OPUS)
description:
n:

Contains the BGM for the danmaku Windows games (6-15) ripped with the default Touhou Music Room settings (1 loop, 5 second linear fade) and the OST for the fighting games.

The following media players should be able to play Opus audio files:

Windows: foobar2000, AIMP, Winamp (with a plug-in), VLC, MPC-HC
Ubuntu: Clementine, Audacious, DeaDBeeF, Lollypop, VLC, mpv
Android: Free: foobar2000 for Android, AIMP for Android, Youki, Capriccio (free with ads, $1 without ads), VLC for Android, MX Player | Paid: GoneMAD, Neutron, Poweramp
iOS: Capriccio (free with ads, $1 without ads)
